method.name: IsInitialized
method.comment: Tests whether the object has been initialized.

method.name: _getdefaultuseragent
method.comment: Returns the default User-Agent used by a WebView. An instance of WebView could use a different User-Agent if a call is made UserAgentString as String.

method.name: _getgetme
method.comment: Gets this class Me variable.

method.name: _gethorizontalfadingedgeenabled
method.comment: Define whether the horizontal edges should be faded when this view is scrolled horizontally. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _getscrollbardefaultdelaybeforefade

method.name: _getscrollbarfadeduration

method.name: _getscrollbarfadingenabled

method.name: _getscrollbarsize

method.name: _getverticalfadingedgeenabled

method.comment: Define whether the vertical scrollbar should be drawn or not. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _importsettingsfrom
method.comment: Import settings from other WebView without referencing.

method.name: _initialize
method.comment: Initializes the object. You can add parameters to this method if needed.

method.name: _setalgorithmicdarkeningallowed
method.comment: Control whether algorithmic darkening is allowed. Added in API level 33

method.name: _setallowcontentaccess
method.comment: Enables or disables content URL access within WebView. Added in API level 11.

method.name: _setallowfileaccess
method.comment: Enables or disables file access within WebView. Added in API level 3.

method.name: _setallowfileaccessfromfileurls
method.comment: Added in API level 16. This method was deprecated in API level 30. This setting is not secure.

method.name: _setallowuniversalaccessfromfileurls
method.comment: Added in API level 16. This method was deprecated in API level 30. This setting is not secure.

method.name: _setappcacheenabled
method.comment: Added in API level 7. This method was deprecated in API level 30. The Application Cache API is deprecated and this method will become a no-op on all Android versions once support is removed in Chromium. Consider using Service Workers instead. See https://web.dev/appcache-removal/ for more information.

method.name: _setappcachemaxsize
method.comment: Added in API level 7. Value in bytes. This method was deprecated in API level 18. Quota is managed automatically; this method is a no-op.

method.name: _setappcachepath
method.comment: Added in API level 7. This method was deprecated in API level 30. The Application Cache API is deprecated and this method will become a no-op on all Android versions once support is removed in Chromium. Consider using Service Workers instead. See https://web.dev/appcache-removal/ for more information.

method.name: _setblocknetworkimage
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView should not load image resources from the network (resources accessed via http and https URI schemes). Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setblocknetworkloads
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView should not load resources from the network. Added in API level 8.

method.name: _setbuiltinzoomcontrols
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView should use its built-in zoom mechanisms. Added in API level 3.

method.name: _setcachemode
method.comment: Overrides the way the cache is used. Values: CACHEMODE_LOAD_DEFAULT, CACHEMODE_LOAD_CACHE_ELSE_NETWORK, CACHEMODE_LOAD_NO_CACHE and CACHEMODE_LOAD_CACHE_ONLY=3. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setcursivefontfamily
method.comment: Sets the cursive font family name. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setdatabaseenabled
method.comment: Sets whether the database storage API is enabled. Added in API level 5.

method.name: _setdatabasepath
method.comment: Added in API level 5. This method was deprecated in API level 19. Database paths are managed by the implementation and calling this method will have no effect.

method.name: _setdefaultfixedfontsize
method.comment: Sets the default fixed font size. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setdefaultfontsize
method.comment: Sets the default font size. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setdefaulttextencodingname
method.comment: Sets the default text encoding name to use when decoding html pages. The default is "UTF-8". Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setdisabledactionmodemenuitems
method.comment: Disables the action mode menu items according to menuItems flag. Values: MENU_ITEM_NONE, MENU_ITEM_SHARE, MENU_ITEM_WEB_SEARCH or MENU_ITEM_PROCESS_TEXT. Added in API level 24.

method.name: _setdisplayzoomcontrols
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView should display on-screen zoom controls when using the built-in zoom mechanisms. Added in API level 11.

method.name: _setdomstorageenabled
method.comment: Sets whether the DOM storage API is enabled. Added in API level 7.

method.name: _setenablesmoothtransition
method.comment: This method was deprecated in API level 17. This method is now obsolete, and will become a no-op in future. Added in API level 11.

method.name: _setfantasyfontfamily
method.comment: Sets the fantasy font family name. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setfixedfontfamily
method.comment: Sets the fixed font family name. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setforcedark
method.comment: Set the force dark mode for this WebView. Values (FORCE_DARK_OFF=0, FORCE_DARK_AUTO=1, FORCE_DARK_ON=2) Added in API level 29. Deprecated in API level 33

method.name: _setgeolocationdatabasepath
method.comment: Added in API level 5. Deprecated in API level 24.

method.name: _setgeolocationenabled
method.comment: Sets whether Geolocation is enabled. Permissions in manifest: Manifest.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION and Manifest.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION. Added in API level 5.

method.name: _sethorizontalscrollbarthumbcolor

method.comment: Defines the horizontal track color. Added in API level 29.

method.name: _setjavascriptcanopenwindowsautomatically
method.comment: Allow JavaScript to open windows automatically. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setlighttouchenabled
method.comment: This method was deprecated in API level 18. From Build.VERSION_CODES.JELLY_BEAN this setting is obsolete and has no effect. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setloadsimagesautomatically
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView should load image resources. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setloadwithoverviewmode
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView loads pages in overview mode, that is, zooms out the content to fit on screen by width. Added in API level 7.

method.name: _setmediaplaybackrequiresusergesture
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView requires a user gesture to play media. Added in API level 17.

method.name: _setminimumfontsize
method.comment: Sets the minimum font size. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setminimumlogicalfontsize
method.comment: Sets the minimum logical font size. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setmixedcontentmode
method.comment: Configures the WebView's behavior when a secure origin attempts to load a resource from an insecure origin. Values (MIXED_CONTENT_ALWAYS_ALLOW=0, MIXED_CONTENT_NEVER_ALLOW=1, MIXED_CONTENT_COMPATIBILITY_MODE=2). Added in API level 21.

method.name: _setneedinitialfocus
method.comment: Tells the WebView whether it needs to set a node to have focus when WebView#requestFocus(int, android.graphics.Rect) is called. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setoffscreenpreraster
method.comment: Sets whether this WebView should raster tiles when it is offscreen but attached to a window. Added in API level 23.

method.name: _setsafebrowsingenabled
method.comment: Sets whether Safe Browsing is enabled. Added in API level 26.

method.name: _setsansseriffontfamily
method.comment: Sets the sans-serif font family name. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setsaveformdata
method.comment: This method was deprecated in API level 26. In Android O and afterwards, this function does not have any effect, the form data will be saved to platform's autofill service if applicable. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setsavepassword
method.comment: This method was deprecated in API level 18. Saving passwords in WebView will not be supported in future versions. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setscrollbarstyle
method.comment: Specify the style of the scrollbars. Values: For example, if a view has a background drawable and you want to draw the scrollbars inside the padding specified by the drawable, you can use SCROLLBARS_INSIDE_OVERLAY or SCROLLBARS_INSIDE_INSET. If you want them to appear at the edge of the view, ignoring the padding, then you can use SCROLLBARS_OUTSIDE_OVERLAY or SCROLLBARS_OUTSIDE_INSET. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setseriffontfamily
method.comment: Sets the serif font family name. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setstandardfontfamily
method.comment: Sets the standard font family name. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setsupportmultiplewindows
method.comment: Sets whether the WebView whether supports multiple windows. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _setsupportzoom

method.name: _settextzoom
method.comment: Sets the text zoom of the page in percent. Added in API level 14.

method.name: _setuseragentstring

method.name: _setusewideviewport
